---
import Section from '../shared/Section.astro';
---

<Section>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center reveal">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary md:text-4xl">
      All software free. Forever.<br/>
      <span class="text-accent">No exceptions.</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      Blueprints are open source. We charge for support, operations, and expertise &mdash; never for access to code. If you leave OpenOva, you keep everything. You just lose the support, the AI operations, and the expert network.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border-primary bg-bg-secondary p-5">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">Exit strategy</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">Do nothing. Blueprints are open source. Walk away and everything keeps running.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border-primary bg-bg-secondary p-5">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">No lock-in</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">No proprietary agents. No vendor forks. Every blueprint is upstream open source and Kustomize-based.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-border-primary bg-bg-secondary p-5">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-accent">Full source access</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-text-secondary">Read every line. Fork if you want. Customize what you need. No black boxes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>
